data.description: Check out this charming home!!!  Updated and ready for move in.  Home features 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, very nice kitchen with an adjoining nook for a dining room table.  Basement is unfinished but could easily be turned into great living space.  Fantastic privacy fence around backyard has a storage shed, playset and a trampoline.  Great location - close to everything.
